snippet.title: SCP: Containment Breach on mobile. [SCP: Site-19.]
snippet.description:
SCP: Site 19 is the mobile game based on SCP Foundation. 
The models & textures are from SCP Containment Breach.
Please support me on Patreon:
https://www.patreon.com/aidynilyas
So I can use some paid assets, pay for the engine license and work on this project full-time. 
Join discord channel:
https://discord.gg/KNBt7DG
To keep up with events and news!
